snippet.title: Second Wave - Beta Gameplay | The Final Two Minutes
snippet.description:
Footage is from the Final Game Match on the first Beta for Second Wave. This took place right before the servers were taken down. A special thanks to all of the players that were a part of our Beta. We can't wait to see you next time! ✨

Welcome to the world of Second Wave, where the battle for supremacy is about to begin! Get ready to dive headfirst into a world that blends the MOBA and TPS / FPS genres into an exhilarating gaming experience unlike any other!

You and your team will engage in intense battles with a variety of game modes, including Domination, Three-Way-Battle and Stone-Grab where you capture or defend arcane stones, and you'll do so with a cast of unique and charming characters, each with their own incredible abilities and fascinating stories waiting to be discovered.
